#. module: coal_petroleum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coal_petroleum.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The company specializes in trading coal and petroleum products, acquiring "
"them from international suppliers or local vendors and reselling them to "
"customers. They have a unique quality-checking method during the procurement "
"process,\n"
"            defining specific parameters in the GRN and Delivery stages to "
"ensure product quality."
msgstr ""
"The company specializes in trading coal and petroleum products, acquiring "
"them from international suppliers or local vendors and reselling them to "
"customers. They have a unique quality-checking method during the procurement "
"process,\n"
"            defining specific parameters in the GRN and Delivery stages to "
"ensure product quality."

